        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2050377556" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16963018074954818518">This is how a presidential biography should be written! Rather than an overly long, tedious account of boring minutiae, just tell the reader the critical events that made the president into the type of leader they became. All I ever really knew about Pres. Jackson was his involvement in the Battle of New Orleans and that he was known as &quot;Old Hickory.&quot; This bio helps you come to know what made Andrew Jackson tick and his unique temperament that sometimes helped his ambition yet caused him grief a</span>
  <span id="freeText16963018074954818518" style="display:none">This is how a presidential biography should be written! Rather than an overly long, tedious account of boring minutiae, just tell the reader the critical events that made the president into the type of leader they became. All I ever really knew about Pres. Jackson was his involvement in the Battle of New Orleans and that he was known as "Old Hickory." This bio helps you come to know what made Andrew Jackson tick and his unique temperament that sometimes helped his ambition yet caused him grief as well. Reading of Jackson's time in office will definitely make you think of modern-day parallels in the current news cycle. Great book!</span>
  <a data-text-id="16963018074954818518" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

